<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Blog de lokhi</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "style", :media => "all" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  </head>
  <body>
   <div class="header">
    <div class="header-box">
      <div class="logo">
        <%= link_to image_tag("logo.png", :alt => "Lokhi Labs"), posts_path, :title => "homepage" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="content-left">
      <%= yield %>
    </div>
    <div class="content-right">
    <%= render 'posts/search_posts' %>
    
    <div class="pres">
      <div class="pres-avatar">
         <%= image_tag "pirate.png" , :alt => "Pirate" %>
      </div>
      <div class="pres-content">
        <p>Bienvenue sur mon blog !</p>
        <br />
        <p>Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Proin ipsum nisi, elementum interdum sodales et, sagittis at metus. Fusce vel erat non nisi molestie aliquet.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="end"></p>
    </div>
    <%= render 'session/session' %>
    <%= render 'posts/last_posts' %>
    <%= render 'comments/last_comments' %>
    <%= link_to image_tag("rss.png", :alt => "rss"), posts_path(:rss), :title => "RSS"  %>
    


    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="end"></p>
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-box">
      <div class="footer-toy">
        &nbsp;
      </div>
      <div class="footer-content">
        Texte du footer
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>
